BofA Investment-Banking Results Improving Since Third Quarter

-- B y   H u g h   S o n
-- 
2011-12-06T14:44:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-06/bofa-investment-banking-results-improving-since-third-quarter.html
Bank of America Corp. (BAC) ’s trading
results have improved in its investment banking unit this
quarter, Chief Executive Officer  Brian T. Moynihan  said.  “We’ve seen better results so far in the fourth quarter
and we’ll see how we finish the year,” Moynihan said today at a
conference in  New York .  To contact the reporter on this story:
